.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我真係會避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我理得你話我歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛面，生到成面一粒粒，唐氏仔我都唔會彈開<br />\n但口up up燥底嗰d一定要走開<br />\n情緒唔穩定好危險</blockquote><br />\n爛面/有疤同唐氏個啲我唔會避 <br />\n但口upup或者自言自語 奇奇怪怪嗰啲我會行開 <br />\n唔係話咩 但有時真係預計唔到佢哋會做咩"},{"pid":"00bdeccdadac76e40e5b2c66f212599ad6e0dae3","tid":117072,"uid":71527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9WgTZbDK1U&amp;t=6m50s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO9WgTZbDK1U%26t%3D6m50s&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ca19617b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9WgTZbDK1U&amp;t=6m50s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片有個阿叔,嘗試拿走自焚者的打火機,結果引火上身,見到痴線佬真係要保持距離</blockquote><br />\n地鐵站間唔中都有d人大聲自言自語行<br />\n但從來無人會走開迴避<br />\n掛住打機聽歌當癲佬小丑食花生<br />\n俾d癲恅隨時拎刀拎野出黎斬死都未知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我完全唔明點解8成人會當佢地冇野企/坐咁近（仲有其他位置企and 坐）<br />\n我第一時間行遠1卡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係唔想接受佢地，係果種危機感令程長途車唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終香港人壓力大，睇落怪怪地嘅人都唔少）"},{"pid":"979a1fd09470bee0bb961e483c9d2067814109cc","tid":117072,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"2ec54f961fdfe34d6edfffb1759027e885b0aa04","tid":117072,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"3f63833cb74ac5aea0d7d66b54eea94c14f5ec61","tid":117072,"uid":24280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常一開頭,   有個人同另一個人郁手 <br />\n身邊既乘客係以為佢地迫得制而打架 ,   係唔會幫任何一方<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">